Hi,
on my ThinkPad X61s, I can not use suspend to RAM anymore. It works
with 2.6.27.
This is what happens:
$ cat /sys/power/state 
mem disk
$ echo mem > /sys/power/state
bash: echo: write error: Device or resource busy
$
